<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(gboolean, gboolean)
@returns(none)
def set_repeat(repeat_x, repeat_y)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Sets whether the @texture should repeat horizontally or
vertically when the actor size is bigger than the image size</p>

<table>
<tr>
<td><p>repeat_x :</p></td>
<td><p>True if the texture should repeat horizontally</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>repeat_y :</p></td>
<td><p>True if the texture should repeat vertically</p></td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>Since 1.0</p>
